LanguageData.Chemical_Planetarium.label: Planetarium
LanguageData.Chemical_Planetarium.description:
Planetarium intake status. 

Rabbies maintain a clear mind and quick intellectual activity thanks to the effect of this ingredient on the brain. 

When these substances are scarce... they don't die, but their minds are miserable. Feed the planetarium again to find the spirit.

This effect will not disappear.
